<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> spine-chilling experience • spine-tingling experience</xh5><p> <i>spine-chilling experience—</i>said of a terrifying event or encounter that happens to a person: Have a <u>spine chilling experience</u> amidst the wildlife sanctuaries where you will see tigers in their natural habitat.</p><p> <i>spine-tingling experience—</i>said of smth. very exciting or thrilling a person gets involved in: It was a <u>spine-tingling experience</u> to hear the call of kiwi in the Wellington hills for the first time in more than a century.</p> </entry>
